descriptionHtml: This is my first mod ever and im very excited to share it with the amazing community. I know its not so great now buuuut I will constantly update it to improve it. Its a simple home for a new player to get started in located in Riverwood next to mill. Has some storage chests and barrels. Nothing should despawn inside this home so its a safe zone. Any advice or comments is very welcomed.
author: United Llamas
